      </view>

      <view class="guide-item">
        <view class="guide-header">
          <text class="guide-icon">📈</text>
          <text class="guide-title">数据统计</text>
        </view>
        <text class="guide-desc">实时查看个人出勤率、缺勤次数等考勤统计数据，支持导出详细报告。</text>
      </view>

      <view class="guide-item">
        <view class="guide-header">
